{"abstract":[{"text":"Customize foreground push notifications when native iOS system alerts are disabled.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Prerequisites","type":"heading","text":"Prerequisites"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Before you begin, ensure you have:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A Pushwoosh account"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A Pushwoosh project set up in your account"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An iOS platform configured in your Pushwoosh project. We recommend using the Token-Based Authentication configuration as the simplest approach"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your Pushwoosh Application Code from the Control Panel","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"iOS 14.0+ deployment target"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pushwoosh SDK version 6.10.0 or higher"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"PushwooshFramework, PushwooshCore, and PushwooshBridge frameworks integrated in your project"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Important","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": PushwooshForegroundPush requires the main Pushwoosh SDK to be properly configured for push notifications."}]}],"style":"note"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Step-1-Disable-Native-Alerts","text":"Step 1: Disable Native Alerts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Add the following key to your ","type":"text"},{"code":"Info.plist","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" file to disable native iOS system alerts:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["<key>Pushwoosh_SHOW_ALERT<\/key>","<false\/>"],"syntax":"xml","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This allows PushwooshForegroundPush to display custom foreground notifications instead of system alerts.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Step 2: Install Module","anchor":"Step-2-Install-Module","type":"heading"},{"tabs":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In Xcode, use the following URL to add the Pushwoosh dependency:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["https:\/\/github.com\/Pushwoosh\/Pushwoosh-XCFramework"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Select the required modules in your target:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Important","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The modules PushwooshFramework, PushwooshCore, PushwooshBridge, PushwooshForegroundPush, and PushwooshLiveActivities are required.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note"}],"title":"Swift Package Manager"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Add to your Podfile:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["pod 'PushwooshXCFramework'","pod 'PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshForegroundPush'"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"ruby"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then run:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"bash","code":["pod install"],"type":"codeListing"}],"title":"CocoaPods"}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"text":"Step 3: Add Required Capabilities","level":2,"anchor":"Step-3-Add-Required-Capabilities","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In Xcode:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Select your target"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Go to ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Signing & Capabilities"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Click ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"+ Capability"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" and add ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Push Notifications"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Click "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"+ Capability"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and add "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Background Modes","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In Background Modes, enable "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Remote notifications"}]},{"type":"text","text":" checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]},{"text":"Step 4: Configure Foreground Push","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Step-4-Configure-Foreground-Push"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Configure foreground push and set delegate in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application(_:didFinishLaunchingWithOptions:)"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import UIKit","import PushwooshFramework","import PushwooshForegroundPush","","@main","class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate, PWForegroundPushDelegate {","","    func application(","        _ application: UIApplication,","        didFinishLaunchingWithOptions launchOptions: [UIApplication.LaunchOptionsKey: Any]?","    ) -> Bool {","","        Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush.foregroundNotificationWith(","            style: .style1,","            duration: 5,","            vibration: .notification,","            disappearedPushAnimation: .balls","        )","","        Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush.delegate = self","","        return true","    }","","    \/\/ MARK: - Push Notification Registration","","    func application(","        _ application: UIApplication,","        didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken deviceToken: Data","    ) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistration(deviceToken)","    }","","    func application(","        _ application: UIApplication,","        didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError error: Error","    ) {","        print(\"Failed to register for remote notifications: \\(error)\")","    }","","    \/\/ MARK: - PWForegroundPushDelegate","","    func didTapForegroundPush(_ userInfo: [AnyHashable: Any]) {","        print(\"Foreground custom push tapped: \\(userInfo)\")","    }","}"]},{"text":"Configuration Parameters","level":3,"anchor":"Configuration-Parameters","type":"heading"},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Parameter","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Type"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"style","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PWForegroundPushStyle"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Visual template for the notification. Currently only "},{"code":".style1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is available"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"duration","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"Int","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Display time in seconds","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"vibration"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"PWForegroundPushHapticFeedback","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Haptic feedback type:"},{"type":"text","text":"• "},{"code":".none","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" – No vibration"},{"type":"text","text":"• "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".light"},{"type":"text","text":" – Subtle feedback"},{"text":"• ","type":"text"},{"code":".medium","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" – Standard feedback","type":"text"},{"text":"• ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".heavy"},{"type":"text","text":" – Strong feedback"},{"text":"• ","type":"text"},{"code":".soft","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" – Gentle feedback"},{"text":"• ","type":"text"},{"code":".rigid","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" – Sharp feedback"},{"type":"text","text":"• "},{"code":".notification","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" – System notification feedback","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"disappearedPushAnimation"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"PWForegroundPushDisappearedAnimation","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Exit animation:","type":"text"},{"text":"• ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".balls"},{"text":" – Explodes into particles","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"• "},{"code":".regularPush","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" – Slides up and fades"}]}]]],"type":"table"},{"type":"heading","text":"Delegate Methods","level":3,"anchor":"Delegate-Methods"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshForegroundPush\/documentation\/PushwooshForegroundPush\/PWForegroundPushDelegate"},{"text":" protocol provides callbacks for foreground push events:","type":"text"}]},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Method","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"didTapForegroundPush(_:)","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Called when user taps on the foreground push notification"}]}]]],"type":"table"},{"anchor":"Customization","type":"heading","text":"Customization","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure appearance globally using static properties:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush.useLiquidView = true","Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush.gradientColors = [.red, .orange, .yellow]","Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush.titlePushColor = .red","Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush.messagePushColor = .white","Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush.usePushAnimation = false"],"syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Available-Properties","type":"heading","text":"Available Properties"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"useLiquidView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" - Enable Liquid Glass effect (requires iOS 26+ and Swift 5.13+)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"gradientColors"},{"type":"text","text":" - Custom gradient background colors"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"backgroundColor"},{"type":"text","text":" - Solid background color"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"titlePushColor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" - Text color for notification title"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"messagePushColor"},{"text":" - Text color for notification message","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"titlePushFont"},{"text":" - Custom font for title","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"messagePushFont"},{"text":" - Custom font for message","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"usePushAnimation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" - Enable or disable show animation","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Platform-Support","level":2,"text":"Platform Support","type":"heading"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inli